Merger
======

A program to merge files into a single file and also split merged files into the original separate files

Installation
------------
	./autogen.sh
	./configure
	make
	make install

Usage
-----
	merge:
		merger [file-01] [file-02] [output-file]
		merger [directory] [output-file]
	split:
		merger -s [merged-file] [output-directory]
